      <div type="letter" xml:id="d4e38">
        <pb n="1" facs="0012_000117_000214_0001.jpg" xml:id="d4e39"/>
        <p>Major David Burford</p>
        <p>Dixon's Springs, Smith Co.</p>
        <p>Tennessee</p>
        <p>From Perkins, Campbell &amp; Co</p>
        <p>dated 15 April &amp; red'd 23 April 1854</p>
        <p>ack receipt from Wharton of $1376 22/100</p>
        <pb n="2" facs="0012_000117_000214_0002.jpg" xml:id="d4e53"/>
        <p>Mail</p>
        <p>New Orleans, 15th April 1854</p>
        <p>Major David Burford</p>
        <p>Dixons Springs Smith Co Tennessee</p>
        <p>Dear Sir,</p>
        <p>we have received from Messrs J. &amp; F.D.R. Wharton of Jackson Miss for your account (in their letter of 10th past) three checks ammounting to  $1,376.22</p>
      </div>
